    			The seed mixer will start working soon and you will be able to create your garden plan as well as order your customized seed mix directly on this website.
    		</p>
    		<p>
    			In the meantime you can show us your interest for our product and get updates on the project by dropping us your email.
    		</p>

    		<%= form_tag commitments_path, :class => 'formulaire-participation' do %>

    		<div>
            	<%= text_field_tag :email, params[:email], placeholder: 'mary@example.com' %>
          	</div>

          	<button type="submit" class="submit-button">Submit</button>
          <% end %>
    	</div>
    	
    </div>
  </div>
